        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/CoastalTown/_scene_mamba.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 4f388b6a-0fe0-4119-a9b3-1792922ce76e).Image",
        "Description": "Good Morning, 47.\r\rYour target is Salvatore Bravauomo, an Italian lawyer residing in Sapienza. A well respected lawyer and family man, he would seem as though he isn&apos;t guilty of any crimes. Our client, Marco Abiatti has received word that Bravuomo is in possesion of some sensitive data belonging to him, and is blackmailing him for it. He has already dispatched his guards to find him and retrieve the data, but has failed and needs our help.\r\rFind and eliminate Bravuomo, \r\rGood luck, 47.",
        "GameVersion": "8.6.0.0",
        "IsPublished": true,
        "Entitlements": [
